{"obj_edit_time":"1724927718","blocks":[{"block_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","block_type":1,"children":["JN1Ad8PZvo2DKixzXY1c1N5HndA","VEljduJbEoxWgqxloAHckAHpnte","Ayefdhqheoibutxd3OAcW2GNnyb","F6TjdC2YXo1uRjx3f1scX4VMnFe","IJiadizseoetG4xWibzcUEdinQg","MhZJdRiA2oNSd7xhgC7cdWecnpd","RaPTdINSioaX4MxCifqcDF6onIb","SFiadjFS3oIBymxN0Ucc0iA6nMd"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1 餘額通","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"JN1Ad8PZvo2DKixzXY1c1N5HndA","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1A 問：餘額通觸發自動贖回規則是什麼？能用作抵扣認購其他基金、申購IPO?","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf"},{"block_id":"VEljduJbEoxWgqxloAHckAHpnte","block_type":2,"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"答：1.基金是每個交易日都會產生申贖渠道單，但是交收（回填）依賴基金公司實際返回申購確認份額，贖回確認金額的時間，基金那邊設定了T+幾只是展示用的；客戶購買了股票，T+2需要交收股票，買完股票後現金可提會變成負數，此時會立刻觸發餘額通自動贖回，T+1基金公司會打款到賬，當天要人工在WBO完成清算交收，這樣客戶帳戶上就有錢作T+2的股票交收了。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Ayefdhqheoibutxd3OAcW2GNnyb","block_type":2,"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"2.理論上不能買基金，因為購買基金當天就要客戶扣款，然後把錢打給基金公司，等不到餘額通贖回。 IPO使用餘額通有時間限制，如果用戶認購IPO時間晚於認購截止日的前一個交易日上午9:00，因為餘額通贖回金額到帳時間晚於認購截止日，就不能用餘額通直接打新，用作抵扣美股港股則沒問題。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"F6TjdC2YXo1uRjx3f1scX4VMnFe","block_type":2,"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"IJiadizseoetG4xWibzcUEdinQg","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"9.1B 問：設置了最小贖回份額為整數，為什麼能贖回小數份額？","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf"},{"block_id":"MhZJdRiA2oNSd7xhgC7cdWecnpd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"答：餘額通標的，贖回時只判斷持股份額，不判斷最小賣出份額/金額限制。\n","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"自動贖回是用於償還欠款或交收的資金，如果無法自動贖回會導致客戶欠款。所以餘額通贖回時不受最小賣出份額/金額的限制。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"RaPTdINSioaX4MxCifqcDF6onIb","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":308,"token":"TX2fboq73ojEFdx34PtckCJ0n2g","width":1640},"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf"},{"block_id":"SFiadjFS3oIBymxN0Ucc0iA6nMd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"Eew3dz2xso9or0xk4OOc8zXVnyf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}